File::Slurp::Unicode
--------------------

This module wraps the standard File::Slurp package and adds character
encoding support.

For full documentation, run:
  perldoc lib/File/Slurp/Unicode.pm


Installation
------------

To build, test and install:

 perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install


